text: Þis is þara VII hidæ boc to west tices tede þe Eadmund cing gebocode Æþelgearde his þegne on ece yrfæ.
Of oddan heale on luhhes geat.
Of luhhes geate on ceorla geat.
Of ceorla geate on risc mære.
On sciteres flodan on nedder heal.
Of nedder heale on þære greatan bechan geat.
Of stapol wege on þæt deor geat.
Of ðam deor geate æft on oddan heal.
